info: Rating, 4 stars,  · August 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: The apartment is really nice and private. It matched exactly with the pictures and it’s worth for the price we paid. However, there could be some improvements. They are very strict with their check out methods. We were supposed to check out at 11 am, and the caretaker came inside exactly at 11 and waited till we left, it was very uncomfortable to get ready and pack everything in front of their care taker. The caretaker was also asking us to wait downstairs for the Uber cause the driver was struggling to find the place which I personally found very inconsiderate. The location is very far from the main city, there are no local shops or restaurants nearby, even food-panda is out of reach in that area. A personal transport is very much needed to enjoy your stay there.
